WEBVTT

30:32.580 --> 30:33.620 line:80%
Is that correct?

30:33.870 --> 30:35.800 line:80%
I encountered bandits on the road,

30:36.080 --> 30:37.320 line:80%
and lost the document
from my place of origin.

30:37.170 --> 30:39.320 line:80%
[Travel Permit]

30:38.380 --> 30:40.920 line:80%
